snippet.title: Wacky Races   3DO gameplay
snippet.description:
Gaming 8-bit days a week!
Intro + short Gameplay vids with no edits. Me playing 3DO games with varying results! I may have to try again and do better next time.
Using 3DO Panasonic FZ-10, Framemeister XRGB, GamecaptureHD, Sharp LCD TV
